<div class="solutions">

  <div class="overview">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="pitch">
          <h2>Live Video-Streaming in iOS</h2>
          <p>
            With the <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/cine-io/cineio-broadcast-ios">cine.io Broadcast iOS SDK</a>,
            you can publish live RTMP streams right from your iPhone or iPad.
            The h.264 and AAC encoding happens in a hardware-accelerated way,
            so you don't need to worry about battery life. Our backend handles
            the conversion to HLS for consumption on any compatible device.
            Both Objective-C and Swift are supported.
          </p>

          <h2>Video-Conferencing in iOS</h2>
          <p>
            With the <a target="_blank" href="#">cine.io Peer iOS SDK</a>,
            you can make and receive calls or join group conferences using
            WebRTC from your iPhone or iPad. We handle all of the signaling
            and identification in a secure and seamless way. Both Objective-C
            and Swift are supported.
          </p>
        </div>
